spec_data.Name: partclone
spec_data.License: GPL+ and GPLv2 and GPLv2+ and GPLv3+ and LGPLv2 and LGPLv2+
spec_data.Description:
Partclone provides utilities to clone and restore used blocks on a partition
and is designed for higher compatibility of the file system by using existing
libraries, e.g. e2fslibs is used to read and write the ext2 partition.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 29 Oct 2017 10:12:51 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Utility to clone and restore a partition
